These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
There 4 different types of food: mango, pepper, pomegranate, raspberry
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, martial-arts, comedy, horror
1. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
2. the person eating mango is the person watching horror movies##1
3. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
4. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
5. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | raspberry | pomegranate | pepper | mango   |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts  | satire     | comedy   | horror |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, cooking, video-games, woodworking
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: rose, azalea, tulip, dahlia
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person who growsazalea##1
2. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who growstulip##1
5. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the person who growsrose##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby   | video-games | woodworking | cooking | camping    |
| Flower   | tulip    | azalea      | rose | dahlia |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
City: san-francisco, colone, berlin, hannover
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, drama, mystery, time-travel
1. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
2. the person traveling to san-francisco is the person watching crime movies##1
3. the person watching drama movies is on the far right##1
4. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
5. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| City         | san-francisco | hannover | berlin   | colone |
| Movie-Genre   | crime   | mystery | time-travel | drama         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-4::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: grey, blue, amber, red
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, sailing, surfing, tennis
1. the person who's sport is sailing is the person who likes red##1
2. the person who likes blue is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
3. the person who likes blue is on the left of the person who likes grey##1
4. the person who likes blue is on the right of the person who likes red##1
5. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Color   | red | blue | grey  | amber      |
| Sport         | sailing | tennis   | surfing | basketball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-5::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: aquamarine, grey, white, lavender
4 different pets are kept: dog, hamster, hedgehog, pony
1. the person who likes grey is on the left of the person who likes aquamarine##1
2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person who likes white##1
3. the person who likes lavender is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
4. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |  2   |    3     |      4      |
| Color   | lavender | white | grey | aquamarine |
| Pet    | dog       | pony | hedgehog | hamster     |

