.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, almond-milk, cola, 7up
4 different pets are kept: fish, frog, goldfish, mouse
1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
3. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
4. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
5. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Beverage   | 7up | cola | hot-chocolate | almond-milk |
| Pet           | fish      | goldfish | mouse | frog    |

