.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-7::.
4 different games are played: backgammon, canasta, whist, snooker
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, ferret, mouse, rat
1. the owner of the mouse is on the far left##1
2. the person playing snooker is on the far right##1
3. the person playing whist is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the ferret is on the far right##1
5. the person playing canasta is on the left of the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |     3     |   4    |
| Game   | whist | canasta | backgammon | snooker  |
| Pet           | mouse | chinchilla | rat       | ferret |

