.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-8::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: grey, lilac, black, chestnut
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, quad-bike, tram, trike
1. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person who likes lilac##1
2. the person driving the trike is the person who likes chestnut##1
3. the person who likes lilac is on the right of the person who likes grey##1
4. the person who likes black is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
5. the person driving the car is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |    3     |    4     |
| Color         | black | grey      | lilac | chestnut |
| Transport   | car          | quad-bike | tram     | trike    |

