.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-9::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, fantasy, spy, zombie
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, prince, bluemaster, ritmeester
1. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1
2. the person watching family movies is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1
3. the person watching zombie movies is on the far right##1
4. the prince-smoker is on the left of the bluemaster-smoker##1
5. the ritmeester-smoker is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |   3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy    | spy       | family | zombie   |
| Cigar     | prince | bluemaster | ritmeester   | montecristo |

