.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate, milk, sprite
City: venice, boston, nizza, edinburgh
1. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
3. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the person traveling to nizza##1
4. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |       3       |   4    |
| Beverage    | cola | milk  | hot-chocolate | sprite |
| City   | edinburgh | nizza | boston          | venice    |

