3. the owner of the frog is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
4. the accountant is on the right of the social-worker##1
5. the owner of the frog is on the right of the accountant##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Job   | social-worker | accountant | firefighter | electrician  |
| Pet           | hedgehog | fish      | frog | ferret |

