4. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
5. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Beverage      | coffee   | soy-milk | cola   | fanta      |
| Sport   | climbing | handball      | water-polo | skateboarding |

