.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-20::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, argentine, mexican, nigerian
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, mirinda, tea, fanta
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the argentine##1
2. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the nigerian##1
3. the american is on the left of the mexican##1
4. the nigerian is the person drinking fanta##1
5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Nationality   | american | mexican | argentine | nigerian   |
| Beverage     | tea  | iced-tea    | mirinda       | fanta |

 